<div class="tldr-box">
  <h3>TL;DR, the short answer for Indians</h3>
  <p>Pick Gemini if Indian payment friction matters (it accepts UPI), if you live inside Gmail and Docs, or if you'd otherwise pay for 2 TB Google One storage. Pick ChatGPT if you want the best image generation, the best advanced voice mode, or a more polished standalone chat experience and you have a forex card. Many Indian users keep ChatGPT free + Gemini Pro, the inverse is also defensible.</p>
</div>

<p>This comparison is written from the perspective of a working Indian, a freelancer, founder, professional, or student, who needs to pick one paid AI subscription. Both ChatGPT and Gemini are excellent in 2026; the right pick depends on a few specific Indian considerations that most global comparisons miss.</p>

<h2>Quick comparison</h2>

